    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>Tapping into your draconic origins, your presence starts to become much more terrifying in your form as a Nirik. This aura is a @Template[type:emanation|distance:10]. An enemy that enters or ends its turn in the aura must attempt a Will save against the higher of your spell DC or class DC. The DC for allies who have travelled with you for a longer period of time is reduced by 5.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is unaffected and temporarily immune to your Frightful Aura for 1 minute.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Frightened]{Frightened 1}</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Frightened]{Frightened 2}</p>",
